{{Han compound|木|反|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=tree}}.

Officially adopted as the simplified form of {{zh-l|*闆}} (etymology 2) in the ''Chinese Character Simplification Scheme'' ({{lw|zh|pref=《|s:漢字簡化方案|漢字簡化方案|suf=》}}) in 1956.

===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms}}
The same word as {{och-l|版|plank}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|འཕར||panel; small plank}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}), {{cog|my|ပြား|t=flat, pya}} ({{zh-ref|Hill, 2019}}, p. 224).

